title: The End Of War [Action, Eng, 2018]
description:
It's April of 1945, the beginning of the offensive on Berlin. You, a Soviet soldier, miraculously survived after your unit was struck hard. You find yourself in a forest where you stumble upon enemy soldiers. You have to break through their posts and find out what they are guarding there.
Key assignments can be changed in the main game menu from the default settings if desired.

WASD - Movement.
R - Recharge.
Q - A cutting weapon.
The character views the mouse cursor. Left mouse click to shoot.

System:

ОС: Windows 7 +
CPU: 2 GHz
RAM: 512 mb
VRAM: 256 mb
HDD: 333 mb
